# AI-Powered Presentation Generation System

## Overview

This project is an end-to-end **Generative AI system** that automatically creates PowerPoint presentations from a single user-provided title.

The system leverages **Large Language Models (LLMs)** for structured slide content generation, **text-to-image diffusion models** for visual enhancement, and programmatic PPT construction to produce ready-to-download presentations with minimal human input.

The project demonstrates **multi-model orchestration**, **pipeline-based design**, and **full-stack GenAI deployment**.

---

## Problem Statement

Creating structured presentations is time-consuming and repetitive. This system automates the entire workflow by:

- Generating a slide outline using an LLM
- Creating slide-wise bullet points
- Generating contextual images using a diffusion model
- Assembling a complete PowerPoint file programmatically

The result is a **fully automated presentation generator** from just a title.

---

## Key Features

- Single-title input → complete PPT output
- Structured slide outlines generated via LLM
- Image generation using Stable Diffusion Turbo
- Automatic bullet formatting and layout handling
- FastAPI backend for generation
- Streamlit-based frontend for user interaction
- Downloadable `.pptx` output

---

## System Architecture

User (Streamlit UI)
└── Title Input
└── FastAPI Backend
└── LLM Slide Outline Generator
└── Slide Titles
└── Bullet Points
└── Image Prompts
└── Image Generation (Stable Diffusion Turbo)
└── PPT Builder (python-pptx)
└── Slides
└── Text Content
└── Images
└── Generated PPT File


---

## Tech Stack

### Backend
- **FastAPI**
- **Python 3.10+**

### LLM & GenAI
- **OpenAI API** (for slide outline generation)
- **GPT-based structured JSON output**
- **Stable Diffusion Turbo** (text-to-image generation)

### Presentation Generation
- **python-pptx**
- Automated slide layout and formatting

### Frontend
- **Streamlit**
- Simple UI for title input and PPT download

---

## Pipeline Breakdown

### 1. LLM-Based Slide Outline
- Generates:
  - Slide titles
  - Bullet points
  - Image prompts
- Enforced JSON structure for reliability

### 2. Image Generation
- Uses Stable Diffusion Turbo
- Generates slide-specific visuals
- Optimized for fast inference

### 3. PPT Assembly
- Title slide + content slides
- Bullet hierarchy handling
- Optional image embedding per slide

### 4. Delivery
- PPT file returned via API
- Downloaded through Streamlit UI

---

## API Endpoint

### Generate Presentation
**Response**
- Returns a downloadable `.pptx` file

## Project Structure

├── gen_ppt/
│ ├── app.py # FastAPI entry point
│ ├── clients.py # OpenAI client configuration
│ ├── llm_outline.py # LLM-based slide outline generator
│ ├── image_generator.py # Stable Diffusion image generation
│ ├── ppt_builder.py # PPT construction logic
│ ├── pipeline.py # End-to-end orchestration
│ ├── ui.py # Streamlit frontend
├── images/ # Generated images
├── requirements.txt
└── README.md